TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
Is the pin still in?

Waiter, there's a Kraken in my soup!!!!!!

No, that's grass coming out of your bog soup.

Waiter,,retiaW

Yes sir,,ris seY

Waiter, Shrek found my hiding spot! Help!

You have reached the voicemail box of ... WAITER ...

Please leave a message after the beep. ... *beep*

Waiter, why is my soup on the floor?

It tastes better that way.

Waiter, why is the Minecraft Steve in my soup.

That's where his spawn point is. Just move your soup away a little bit and kill Steve :^3

Waiter, there's badly engineered stuff in my soup. >:-[

That's ice cream. You ordered the caramel soup, sir.

Waiter, there's a missile flying through my soup at 300,000,000 m/s!

That's a nu

Waiter, there's fallout in my soup!

Would you like the General Rarity edition or the Original edition?

Waiter, there's a black hole in my soup!

What soup?

Waiter there is an eyeball in my soup.

No that's a potato dummy.

Waiter why is there a hand in my soup.

That's the HANDy soup, sir. Haha, get it? [loud boos emanate from the other tables]

Waiter! There's a mouse in my soup!

`

Edited February 7, 2021 by LVL 9001

Fair enough.

Waiter!!!! I'm in my soup!

Don't forget to eat it.

Waiter, there's a giant block of salt in my soup!

That's the Ocean soup you ordered.

Waiter, there's a floating dead kerbal that is being eaten by a mini-kraken in my soup!

If you don't eat your soup now, there'll be two dead kerbals.

Waiter! There is something in my soup, but I forgot what it was!

Sir, it seems you have found our mystery goo, would you like that packaged to go?

Waiter! Theres solid rocket fuel in my soup!

Be careful - once you press the spacebar, the fuel will ignite and you bowl will fly straight into your mouth. This bowl can not be shut down, it will probably stop when it's fuel is depleted. But once in your mouth, there will be an explosion of flavors.

Waiter! There is a Limit Theory in my soup!

I see..I seems like it is generating strange things out of an unknown algorithm..

Waiter ! There is a wireless webcam in my soup !

You dropped your phone, sir.

Waiter, there's a kerbal in my soup!

Well, at least he isn't dead this time.

Waiter! There is a dying forum game in my soup!

Hold on, i'll stab that pesky persistent forum game with a knife.

Waiter, there's giraffe noises coming out of my soup! >:-[

No that is just the chef.

Waiter, there's a hiroshima bomb in my soup!

DUCK AND COVER!

Waiter, there's an iPhone in my soup!
